#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/polynomial/chebyshev.py:docstring
#: of numpy.polynomial.chebyshev.chebgauss:4
msgid ""
"Computes the sample points and weights for Gauss-Chebyshev quadrature. These "
"sample points and weights will correctly integrate polynomials of degree :"
"math:`2*deg - 1` or less over the interval :math:`[-1, 1]` with the weight "
"function :math:`f(x) = 1/\\sqrt{1 - x^2}`."
msgstr ""

